# Client & GUI tasks

## (GUI) Authentication
- [ ] Allow user to log in only once.
- [ ] Always remember to close the socket when the client stops.
- [ ] Send request to end anonymous chat before the client send log out request.

## (GUI) These functionalities must be accessible only to users who are logged in:
- [ ] Sign up.
- [ ] Chat.
- [ ] Logout.

